../../../../runtime/logs/codex-patlas-beyond-de-giorgi-step-008-explorer-001.log:2067:**The key structural choice:** Lin replaces CKN's direct quantitative energy estimates (explicit cutoff-function PDE estimates) with a **contradiction + compactness** argument. The proof is by contradiction: assuming a sequence of "almost-singular" points exists, Lin derives a contradiction by passing to a limit and using properties of the limiting solution.
