+- `missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-009/winning-chain.md`
+- `missions/beyond-de-giorgi/controller/decisions/decision-021.md`
+
+## Constraints
+
+- do not promote any active candidate reformulation;
+- keep novelty tests in the frozen burden currency rather than free-floating
+  stylistic language;
+- label substantive claims `[VERIFIED]`, `[INFERRED]`, or `[PROPOSED]`.
