+## Endpoint Memo
+
+- `[VERIFIED]` Why the primary endpoint is the right first theorem-facing
+  window:
+  the only locally frozen theorem floor remains suitable weak /
+  Leray-Hopf plus LEI with the CKN/Lin epsilon-regularity contradiction
