+## Scope-Lock Sheet
+
+| item | frozen choice | status | why it is admissibly frozen |
+| --- | --- | --- | --- |
+| primary endpoint family | `local concentration exclusion / endpoint-regularity exclusion on the inherited LEI / CKN ledger` | `[INFERRED]` | Run-009 requires one inherited theorem-facing endpoint on the suitable-weak / LEI floor, and the local record repeatedly privileges concentration exclusion as the honest first endpoint inside the CKN/Lin contradiction package |
+| backup endpoint family | `continuation / near-coercive norm-level control`, reserve only | `[INFERRED]` | The inherited record treats continuation as stricter than concentration exclusion and allows it only after norm-like behavior appears; this keeps exactly one harder reserve without reopening a menu |
+| theorem-facing baseline burden | full localized LEI cutoff-flux bundle `I_flux[phi] = ∬ (|u|^2 + 2p) u · ∇phi` under the shared CKN-style cutoff protocol | `[VERIFIED]` | This is the fixed bad term already frozen by the inherited exact-rewrite architecture and it is the unique place where localized nonlinear transport and pressure transport are charged together |
+| admissible gain notion | positive-margin smaller effective coefficient on the full `I_flux[phi]` bundle after pressure, commutator, reconstruction, and admissibility debt | `[VERIFIED]` | The exact-rewrite screening packet already fixes `coefficient shrinkage in the fixed localized LEI balance` as the only non-decorative gain currency |
+| typed burden ledger | derivative count, locality, cancellation, integrability, pressure recoverability, admissibility, compactness input, scaling compatibility | `[INFERRED]` | Each currency now has a fixed meaning relative to the same theorem-facing burden and later steps must post gains/debts into those explicit columns |
+| same-currency comparability rule | direct comparison only on the same full `I_flux[phi]` object, same solution class, same localization regime, and same charged debt | `[INFERRED]` | This blocks silent comparison between incomparable surrogate gains |
+| transfer-lemma rule | every cross-currency claim must explicitly imply a smaller full-bundle coefficient on `I_flux[phi]` after debt | `[INFERRED]` | Derivative, integrability, surrogate-cancellation, or compactness claims do not count until they are translated back to the frozen burden currency |
+| solution class | suitable weak solutions in the Leray-Hopf energy class with LEI | `[VERIFIED]` | This remains the only locally frozen theorem-facing floor on disk |
+| localization regime | one shared CKN-style parabolic cylinder and one smooth cutoff inside one localized LEI package | `[VERIFIED]` | The inherited rewrite audit already fixes this protocol and requires every later candidate to pay localization costs inside it |
+| anti-repackaging classifier | `equivalent redistribution`, `ambiguous redistribution`, `potentially live mechanism change` | `[INFERRED]` | The classifier is now written in the branch's own LEI burden currency rather than as a style judgment |
+| nearest-prior-art audit format | one fixed packet naming closest comparator, shared structure, exact mathematical delta, improved ledger entry, charged debt, same-currency cash-out or transfer lemma, and final classification | `[INFERRED]` | This is explicit enough to expose absorbed reformulations before promotion |
+
+## Endpoint Memo
+
+- `[VERIFIED]` Why the primary endpoint is the right first theorem-facing
+  window:
+  the only locally frozen theorem floor remains suitable weak /
+  Leray-Hopf plus LEI with the CKN/Lin epsilon-regularity contradiction
+  package, so the honest first endpoint is concentration-style
+  endpoint-exclusion on that inherited ledger rather than a new framework.
+- `[INFERRED]` Why the backup endpoint is the right reserve:
+  continuation / norm-level control is a stricter reserve that the record
+  allows only after a candidate already behaves like near-coercive control.
+  Keeping exactly this reserve prevents an artificially rigid single line
+  without reopening a soft endpoint portfolio.
+- `[VERIFIED]` What kinds of gains count at this interface:
+  only gains that return, after full debt, to a smaller effective coefficient
+  on the full localized `I_flux[phi]` bundle inside the inherited LEI package.
+- `[VERIFIED]` What kinds of gains are decorative:
+  prettier identities before localization;
+  derivative-count or exponent language with no same-ledger cash-out;
+  variable changes that only redistribute the same burden;
+  or gains that require leaving the fixed solution class or cutoff protocol.
+
+## Burden-Ledger Memo
+
+- `[VERIFIED]` Baseline burden in concrete theorem-facing language:
+  the full localized LEI cutoff-flux bundle
+  `I_flux[phi] = ∬ (|u|^2 + 2p) u · ∇phi`
+  under one shared CKN-style cutoff protocol.
+- `[VERIFIED]` Admissible gain notion:
+  positive-margin smaller effective coefficient on that same full bundle after
+  pressure recovery, projection/CZ, commutator, reconstruction, and
+  admissibility debt are charged.
+- `[INFERRED]` Burden currencies:
+  derivative count records whether a derivative reduction survives back to the
+  live LEI estimate;
+  locality records whether the gain acts on the full bundle or only a local
+  surrogate;
+  cancellation records exact sign/null-structure savings on the same bundle;
+  integrability records any space/exponent improvement awaiting transfer;
+  pressure recoverability records pressure-reentry and projection debt;
+  admissibility records host-class and regularity debt;
+  compactness input records any extra extraction/rigidity machinery imported;
+  scaling compatibility records whether the claim respects the inherited LEI /
+  CKN scaling and shared cutoff protocol.
+- `[INFERRED]` Same-currency comparison is sufficient when two candidate claims
+  act on the same full `I_flux[phi]` object under the same solution class,
+  localization regime, and charged debt.
+- `[INFERRED]` A transfer lemma is mandatory whenever the claimed gain lives in
+  any different currency from the baseline burden. Without an explicit
+  theorem-level transfer back to a smaller full-bundle coefficient, the claim
+  remains unresolved and does not count.
+
+## Anti-Repackaging And Prior-Art Memo
+
+- `[INFERRED]` `equivalent redistribution`:
+  after localization, pressure recovery, reconstruction, admissibility debt,
