+  specific transfer lemma whose conclusion is exactly that same gain.
+- `[INFERRED]` Minimum evidence needed to avoid immediate prior-art absorption:
+  one nearest comparator on the local record;
+  one sentence naming the shared exact structure;
+  one exact mathematical delta;
+  one improved frozen ledger entry after debt;
+  and one same-currency cash-out or explicit transfer lemma.
+- `[INFERRED]` Frozen prior-art audit format for later candidate packets:
+  `candidate reformulation / unknown`;
+  `nearest known comparator on the repository record`;
+  `shared exact structure already present there`;
+  `claimed mathematical delta`;
+  `baseline burden entry being improved`;
+  `debt ledger entries charged immediately`;
+  `same-currency cash-out on full I_flux[phi] or explicit transfer lemma`;
+  `anti-repackaging classification`;
+  `prior-art absorption verdict`.
+
+## Step Verdict
