+## Scope-Lock Sheet
+
+| item | frozen choice | status | why it is admissibly frozen |
+| --- | --- | --- | --- |
+| primary endpoint family | `local concentration exclusion / endpoint-regularity exclusion on the inherited LEI / CKN ledger` | `[INFERRED]` | Run-009 requires one inherited theorem-facing endpoint on the suitable-weak / LEI floor, and the local record repeatedly privileges concentration exclusion as the honest first endpoint inside the CKN/Lin contradiction package |
+| backup endpoint family | `continuation / near-coercive norm-level control`, reserve only | `[INFERRED]` | The inherited record treats continuation as stricter than concentration exclusion and allows it only after norm-like behavior appears; this keeps exactly one harder reserve without reopening a menu |
